title: Yannis Pappas - Tale of 2 Coronas
itunes:title: Yannis Pappas - Tale of 2 Coronas
description:
My HoneyDew this week is half of The History Hyenas, Covid survivor, and new dad Yannis Pappas! Yannis and I talk about our battles with Covid and how it affects every person differently. As of this episode, I still don’t have smell, I hardly have any taste, I get tired easily and my brain is foggy. Corona is no joke but we sure as hell figured out a way to laugh about it! Stay safe out there y’all!
